message.command_pending:
Read the following before continuing.
- common: {common_role}
- task_author: {task_author_role}
- personas manifest: {personas_manifest}

command file: {command_file}
agent-comm root: {repo_root}
dashboard: {dashboard_url}

Create the investigation and analyst research tasks first, then use the completed `result_artifact_path` files to break the work down into implementation tasks.

command:
{command_text}

message.coordinator_boot:
Initialization only. This is not a user request.
Read the following to understand your role.
- common: {common_role}
- coordinator: {coordinator_role}

agent-comm root: {repo_root}
dashboard: {dashboard_url}

Do not create a command from this boot message.
When an actual user request arrives later, create the command with {write_command_path}, then wait.

message.question_open:
User input is required.
question_id: {question_id}
task_id: {task_id}
asked_by: {asked_by}
file: {question_file}

{question}

message.reinject:
+Reinjection. Re-read the following.
- common: {common_role}
- role: {role_path}

agent-comm root: {repo_root}
{extra_block}

message.report_generic_complete:
Task completion notification.
task_id: {task_id}
persona: {persona}
type: {task_type}
result: {result}
command_id: {command_id}

message.report_research_complete:
A research task has completed.
task_id: {task_id}
persona: {persona}
result: {result}
command_id: {command_id}
artifact: {artifact}

Review the artifact, but do not create implementation tasks until both the investigation and analyst tasks for this command have completed.

message.report_research_summary:
Read the following before continuing.
- common: {common_role}
- task_author: {task_author_role}
- personas manifest: {personas_manifest}

agent-comm root: {repo_root}
dashboard: {dashboard_url}

Completed investigation / analyst tasks are available. Check the following result files and decompose the next implementation tasks.
{summary_lines}

message.report_review_group_update:
The overall review completed.
task_id: {task_id}
result: {result}
review_decision: {review_decision}
command_id: {command_id}
reviewer_count: {reviewer_count}
rework_note: {note_path}

Create the next rework task if needed.

message.report_reviewer_update:
The review task was updated.
task_id: {task_id}
result: {result}
review_decision: {review_decision}
command_id: {command_id}

Create a rework task if needed.

message.report_tester_update:
The test execution task was updated.
task_id: {task_id}
result: {result}
command_id: {command_id}

Create the next review task if needed.

message.task_author_boot:
Initialization only. This is not a command.
Read the following to understand your role.
- common: {common_role}
- task_author: {task_author_role}
- personas manifest: {personas_manifest}

agent-comm root: {repo_root}
dashboard: {dashboard_url}

Do not create tasks from this boot message.
Wait until coordinator or dispatcher sends the next instruction.

message.worker_boot:
Initialization only. This is not a task.
Read the following to understand your role.
- common: {common_role}
- worker: {worker_role}
- default persona: {persona_role}

worker id: {worker_id}
agent-comm root: {repo_root}
dashboard: {dashboard_url}

Do not start work from this boot message.
Wait until dispatcher sends you a task file.

message.worker_task:
Read the following before starting work.
- common: {common_role}
- worker role: {worker_role}
- persona: {persona_role}

task file: {task_file}
task id: {task_id}
agent-comm root: {repo_root}

Use {task_finish_path} when you complete the task.
Use {create_question_path} if you need to ask a question.
